    <item>
      <title>印尼企业 Mr DIY 计划首次公开募股，募资额高达 2.97 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/mr-diy-s-indonesian-business-ipo-seeks-up-to-297-million-in-december-listing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Mr DIY Group (M) Bhd. 的印尼姊妹公司将通过首次公开募股在雅加达上市，旨在筹集高达 4.7 万亿卢比（2.97 亿美元），这将是该国一年多以来最大规模的上市交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/mr-diy-s-indonesian-business-ipo-seeks-up-to-297-million-in-december-listing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 03:24:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大日本印刷称 Elliott 已出售其大部分股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/dai-nippon-printing-says-elliott-has-sold-most-of-its-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大日本印刷株式会社 (Dai Nippon Printing Co.) 表示，Elliott Investment Management 似乎大幅减持了该公司股份，而这距离该激进基金购买该公司股份还不到两年。该消息导致该公司股价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/dai-nippon-printing-says-elliott-has-sold-most-of-its-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 03:04:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国指控引发股价暴跌后，阿达尼宣称拥有充足现金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/adani-touts-sufficient-cash-after-rout-sparked-by-us-charges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度阿达尼集团表示，其拥有足够的现金来偿还债务，此前美国对创始人高塔姆·阿达尼的贿赂起诉引发了该集团股票和债券的抛售，该集团试图安抚债权人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/adani-touts-sufficient-cash-after-rout-sparked-by-us-charges</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 02:31:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《Kini》称斯沃琪在马来西亚因同性恋骄傲游行手表抢劫案胜诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/swatch-wins-malaysia-suit-over-pride-watch-seizure-kini-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《当今大马》报道，瑞士手表制造商斯沃琪集团 (Swatch Group AG) 赢得了对马来西亚政府的诉讼，该诉讼涉及去年在东南亚国家扣押其以同志骄傲为主题的手表，引发了争议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/swatch-wins-malaysia-suit-over-pride-watch-seizure-kini-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 02:27:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>流动性紧张之际，万达寻求延长 4 亿美元债券发行期限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/wanda-seeks-to-extend-400-million-bond-amid-liquidity-strains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大连万达商业管理集团股份有限公司旗下一家子公司提议对其 2025 年到期的美元债券制定新的条款以延长其期限，此举反映出该中国公司在中国房地产市场低迷时期面临的流动性挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/wanda-seeks-to-extend-400-million-bond-amid-liquidity-strains</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 02:24:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员将注意力转向美联储下一步行动，黄金价格暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/gold-steady-after-surging-last-week-on-escalation-of-ukraine-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员们忽略了美元走软并将注意力转向美联储即将公布的利率决定，黄金价格在上周创下 20 个月来最大涨幅后出现下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/gold-steady-after-surging-last-week-on-escalation-of-ukraine-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 00:16:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受地缘政治风险影响，油价上周飙升后回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-25</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于乌克兰和中东的地缘政治风险令投资者感到不安，油价在上周创下近两个月来最大涨幅后小幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-25</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 23:31:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票、债券价格因交易员青睐 Bessent 而上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/dollar-falls-as-treasury-pick-tempers-trump-bets-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股票和国债价格上涨，交易员对唐纳德·特朗普选择斯科特·贝森特担任财政部长表示欢迎，认为这一慎重选择将为美国经济和金融市场注入更多稳定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/dollar-falls-as-treasury-pick-tempers-trump-bets-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 22:39:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿达尼指控特朗普试图让印度留在美国轨道上的愿望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/adani-charges-to-test-trump-s-desire-to-keep-india-in-us-orbit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2018年，中国科技巨头华为技术有限公司一名高管因违反美国法律被捕，此举震惊了国家主席习近平的核心圈子，并引发了人们对唐纳德·特朗普是否会介入此案的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/adani-charges-to-test-trump-s-desire-to-keep-india-in-us-orbit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美团、周大福的业绩将为中国消费者信心提供线索</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/meituan-chow-tai-fook-earnings-to-offer-clues-on-china-consumer-sentiment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美团和周大福珠宝集团有限公司的业绩应该能反映出中国消费市场的状况，经济复苏缓慢、房地产市场长期低迷以及就业环境不稳定打压了消费者信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/meituan-chow-tai-fook-earnings-to-offer-clues-on-china-consumer-sentiment</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
